    "Annotators are all from Asia, with using English as their sec-ond language.",
    "Since the minimum hourly wage is approximately $7.5, we compensated each annotator with $23, considering the task does not exceed three hours.",
    "Our main concern related to ethical considerations lies within the deployment of the SFT model, particularly when it is trained with a toxic control token.",
    "While users have the capacity to avoid the generation of unsafe responses by refraining from employing the toxic control token, it is still possible to inadvertently activate the model's inherent toxicity.",
    "Moreover, the potential for the model's exploitation for malicious purposes cannot be overlooked."
